              <CheckCircle2 className="size-4 shrink-0 translate-y-0.5 text-primary" />
              <div>
                <p className="font-medium">Review & approve to begin</p>
                <p className="mt-0.5 text-xs text-muted-foreground">
                  The agent will generate one MCQ per objective. You'll get
                  hints and explanations, and can ask follow-up questions at any
                  time.
